response.about:
One day, you have to leave the cool earth
One day, you have to leave your lovely family
One day, you have to leave your dear friends
One day you have to leave everything what you have.
So, before you leave ,
do something good for everyone
because
it will bring happiness to you
and to those
you leave behind.

... In the nature of people lies sadness and depression if things do not happen in the way they want, as well as satisfaction and exaltation when things happen exactly according to their expectations.
The wise can go through difficult and pleasant moments in equilibrium ...
(authors unknown)
